&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Follow the steps to activate developer mode on your Roku device. Save the IP address at the end of the process (&lt;em&gt;example: &lt;code&gt;http://10.1.168.265&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enter the following IP address in a web browser, log-in with username &lt;code&gt;rokudev&lt;/code&gt; and the password you set during the developer mode process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Take any of the .zip files and upload/install to the developer application installer. Your Roku device will load the sample channel instantly.&lt;/p&gt;
